      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HEROIC HENRY (8) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing seventh (24.89) last time in a Mix 5 at Rockhampton. Goes very well here at the trip finding the frame in each of three starts. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Worth another chance. CLEAN ENGINES (3) shapes well for this on his sharp win a few runs back, getting around Capalaba over 366m in 19.83 then hitting the frame in both runs since. Rates a leading chance if runs up to recent winning time. WEBLEC JEWEL (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (22.11) at this track behind My Ernie Jay in a Mix 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to her name from seven starts. Expected to be in this for a long way. MUSCOVITE MICA (2) warrants respect with the drop in journey.",
